Invocation Name: daily christian quotes
des:
Start your day with a bit of Christian wisdom. To open the skill, ask Alexa to "open Daily Christian Quotes."
 To request the addition or removal of a quote, email the developer at winkelmanlogan2@gmail.com.

When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
